			<span class="kicker">AVAILABILITY BIAS</span>
		
	<h1 itemprop="headline">The psychology of why 94 deaths from terrorism are scarier than 301,797 deaths from guns</h1>	<div class="item-meta-mobile"><div class="byline item-meta-row">
	<h5>Written by</h5>

	
		
			
			<a href="https://qz.com/author/jandersonqz/" class="author-name" data-index="0">Jenny Anderson</a>

			
			
			
		
		
	</div>


