			&lt;img src="https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/rtr2r5qg.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=320" alt="Supporters at a &amp;quot;Freedom Rally&amp;quot; wave U.S. flags in support of not building a mosque near Ground Zero..." title=""&gt;
		</noscript>
	</picture>
	<figcaption class="featured-image-caption">
